    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-assessment-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. The six not-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out under MRL 2 provisions. The CFD model is judged credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. The relative hemolysis index criterion (RH < 1) is met across all five evaluated operating points. The assessment team accepts the model for the stated context of use.",
